Subject: Re: [T2] do I need that thermostat?

Thermostats are installed to help get the engine to
operating temp, if the flaps are left open the engine
will not get to the correct temp very fast. It works
best in cold weather. In a warm climate it may not
make much difference, but in a cold climate it could
hurt the engine. Phil

